These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: writing, drawing
Job: security-guard, engineer
1. Job:security-guard is in an even position##4
2. Job:engineer == Hobby:drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | drawing | writing |
| Job     | engineer    | security-guard   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: almond-milk, water
Sport: parkour, ice-hockey
1. Sport:parkour is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:water is on the left of Beverage:almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | water | almond-milk        |
| Sport      | parkour  | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
